  "text": "Definition 19 (see [CITATION_1] ). A matrix ∈ (C) is Hermitian if = * , where * is a conjugate transpose matrix of . A Hermitian matrix ∈ (C) is positive definite if * > 0 for all nonzero ∈ C , and it is positive semidefinite if * ≥ 0 for all nonzero ∈ C .",
